  "html": "<h1>Layer2</h1>\n<div class=\"blocks\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### OntologyBlock</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"layer2-ontology\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:class:: mv:Layer2</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:physicality:: ConceptualEntity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-11\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:role:: Concept</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-12\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">## About Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">A component of the metaverse ecosystem.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### Original Content</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">A secondary protocol or framework built on top of a Layer 1 blockchain (mainnet) that processes transactions off-chain or in parallel, then periodically commits state changes to the main chain, achieving higher throughput and lower fees while inheriting base layer security.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:Layer2))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Layer2 :ScalingSolution)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Defining characteristics</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">EquivalentClasses(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectIntersectionOf(:ScalingSolution</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:buildsOn :Layer1Blockchain)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:inheritsSecurityFrom :Layer1Blockchain)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:settlesTo :Layer1Blockchain)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:throughputMultiplier</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DatatypeRestriction(xsd:decimal</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-7-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:minInclusive &quot;10&quot;^^xsd:decimal))))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Must build on Layer 1</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:buildsOn :Layer1Blockchain))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">FunctionalObjectProperty(:buildsOn)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-11\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Must inherit security from base layer</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-12\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:inheritsSecurityFrom :Layer1Blockchain))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-13\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Must settle to Layer 1</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-14\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:settlesTo :Layer1Blockchain))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-15\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Must have bridge mechanism</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-16\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:hasBridge :BridgeMechanism))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-17\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Data constraints</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-18\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:throughputMultiplier</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DatatypeRestriction(xsd:decimal</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:minInclusive &quot;10&quot;^^xsd:decimal</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:maxInclusive &quot;10000&quot;^^xsd:decimal))))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-19\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:feeReduction</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DatatypeRestriction(xsd:decimal</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:minInclusive &quot;0.9&quot;^^xsd:decimal</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:maxInclusive &quot;0.999&quot;^^xsd:decimal))) # 90-99.9% reduction</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-20\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:finalityTime</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DatatypeRestriction(xsd:decimal</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:minExclusive &quot;0&quot;^^xsd:decimal)))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-21\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Disjoint major categories</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-22\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DisjointClasses(:Rollup :StateChannel :Sidechain :Plasma)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-23\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-24\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**buildsOn**: Layer2 → Layer1Blockchain (required, functional)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-25\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**inheritsSecurityFrom**: Layer2 → Layer1Blockchain (required)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-26\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**settlesTo**: Layer2 → Layer1Blockchain (required, functional)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-27\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**hasBridge**: Layer2 → BridgeMechanism (required, at least 1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-28\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**usesProofSystem**: Layer2 → ProofSystem (required for Rollups)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-29\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**hasSequencer**: Layer2 → Sequencer (0..*)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-30\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**supportsEVM**: Layer2 → EVMCompatibility (0..1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-31\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**throughputMultiplier**: xsd:decimal (10x-10000x of L1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-32\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**feeReduction**: xsd:decimal (0.9-0.999, i.e., 90-99.9%)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-33\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**finalityTime**: xsd:decimal (seconds)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-34\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**withdrawalDelay**: xsd:decimal (seconds, challenge period)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-35\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**transactionsPerSecond**: xsd:decimal (&gt; 1000)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-36\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**securityModel**: xsd:string</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-37\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**dataAvailability**: xsd:string</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-38\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-39\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Rollups must use proof system</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-40\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Rollup</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:usesProofSystem :ProofSystem))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-41\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Optimistic Rollups have challenge period</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-42\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:OptimisticRollup</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:withdrawalDelay</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DatatypeRestriction(xsd:decimal</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:minInclusive &quot;86400&quot;^^xsd:decimal))) # At least 1 day</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-43\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># ZK-Rollups have instant finality</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-44\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ZKRollup</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:finalityTime</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DatatypeRestriction(xsd:decimal</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:maxInclusive &quot;60&quot;^^xsd:decimal))) # Under 1 minute</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-45\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># State channels require multi-party agreement</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-46\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:StateChannel</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:requiresAgreement :MultiPartyConsensus))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-47\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Sidechains have independent consensus</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-48\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Sidechain</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:hasConsensus :IndependentConsensus))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-49\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># EVM compatibility enables smart contract migration</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-50\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectIntersectionOf(:Layer2</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:supportsEVM :EVMCompatibility))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:supports :SoliditySmartContract))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-51\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-52\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-53\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Major Categories</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-54\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:Rollup))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-55\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Rollup :Layer2)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-56\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:StateChannel))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-57\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:StateChannel :Layer2)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-58\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:Sidechain))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-59\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Sidechain :Layer2)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-60\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:Plasma))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-61\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Plasma :Layer2)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-62\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Rollup Types</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-63\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:OptimisticRollup))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-64\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:OptimisticRollup :Rollup)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-65\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:OptimisticRollup</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:usesProofSystem :FraudProof))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-66\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:ZKRollup))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-67\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ZKRollup :Rollup)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-68\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ZKRollup</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:usesProofSystem :ValidityProof))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-69\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># ZK-Rollup Variants</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-70\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ZKSync :ZKRollup)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-71\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:StarkNet :ZKRollup)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-72\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:PolygonZKEVM :ZKRollup)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-73\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Optimistic Rollup Variants</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-74\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Arbitrum :OptimisticRollup)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-75\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Optimism :OptimisticRollup)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-76\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-77\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-78\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:ProofSystem))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"bloc